it.apice.sapere.api.ecolaws.match
Interface MatchResult

All Known Subinterfaces:
MutableMatchResult, ScoredMatchResult
All Known Implementing Classes:
MatchResultImpl, ScoredMatchResultImpl
public interface MatchResult

This interface models an entity which will contain all assignments made during matching phase.

Author:
Paolo Contessi

lookup

Term<?> lookup(VarTerm<?> var)

Asks what term has been assigned to a specific value.

This method does not modify the variable; in order to create the binding assign(var) should be used.

Returns:
The value to be assigned (as a Term)
